T1  - Nicotinamide riboside combined with exercise to treat hypertension in middle-aged and older adults: a pilot randomized clinical trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s11357-025-01815-2
A1  - Lin, Yi
A1  - Zeidan, Rola S
A1  - Lapierre-Nguyen, Stephanie
A1  - Costello, Hannah M
A1  - Anton, Stephen D
A1  - Buford, Thomas W
A1  - Christou, Demetra D
A1  - Gumz, Michelle L
A1  - Leeuwenburgh, Christiaan
