T1  - Effects of NAD+ supplementation with oral nicotinamide riboside on vascular health and cognitive function in older adults with peripheral artery disease: Results from a pilot 4-week open-label clinical trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jpet.2025.103607
A1  - Szarvas, Zsofia
A1  - Reyff, Zeke A
