T1  - NAD+ metabolism restriction boosts high-dose melphalan efficacy in patients with multiple myeloma.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1182/bloodadvances.2024013425
A1  - Soncini, Debora
A1  - Becherini, Pamela
A1  - Ladisa, Francesco
A1  - Ravera, Silvia
