T1  - Safety of Upadacitinib in Immune-Mediated Inflammatory Diseases: Systematic Literature Review of Indirect and Direct Treatment Comparisons of Randomized Controlled Trials.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s12325-023-02732-6
A1  - Mysler, Eduardo
A1  - Burmester, Gerd R
A1  - Saffore, Christopher D
A1  - Liu, John
A1  - Wegrzyn, Lani
