T1  - Bimekizumab treatment in patients with active axial spondyloarthritis: 52-week efficacy and safety from the randomised parallel phase 3 BE MOBILE 1 and BE MOBILE 2 studies.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/ard-2023-224803
A1  - Baraliakos, Xenofon
A1  - Deodhar, Atul
