T1  - Long-term clinical outcomes of certolizumab pegol treatment in non-radiographic axial spondyloarthritis stratified by baseline MRI and CRP status.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/rmdopen-2023-003884
A1  - Rudwaleit, Martin
A1  - Deodhar, Atul
