T1  - Experience with 2 years' intervention to progressively reduce salt supply to kitchens in elderly care facilities-challenges and further research: post hoc analysis of the DECIDE-Salt randomized clinical trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s12916-023-03130-z
A1  - Yuan, Yifang
