T1  - Bempegaldesleukin Plus Nivolumab in Untreated Advanced Melanoma: The Open-Label, Phase III PIVOT IO 001 Trial Results.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1200/JCO.23.00172
A1  - Diab, Adi
A1  - Gogas, Helen
A1  - Sandhu, Shahneen
A1  - Long, Georgina V
