T1  - [Evaluation of the efficacy and safety of Nocardia rubra cell wall skeleton immunotherapy for cervical high-risk HPV persistent infection].
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3760/cma.j.cn112141-20230331-00154
A1  - Chen, F
A1  - Di, W
A1  - Hu, Y J
A1  - Li, C Z
