T1  - The acute effect of different NAD+ precursors included in the combined metabolic activators.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.freeradbiomed.2023.05.032
A1  - Li, Xiangyu
A1  - Yang, Hong
A1  - Jin, Han
A1  - Turkez, Hasan
A1  - Ozturk, Gurkan
A1  - Doganay, Hamdi Levent
