T1  - Longitudinal metabolomics analysis reveals the acute effect of cysteine and NAC included in the combined metabolic activators.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.freeradbiomed.2023.05.013
A1  - Yang, Hong
A1  - Li, Xiangyu
A1  - Jin, Han
A1  - Turkez, Hasan
