T1  - Effect of Sevelamer versus Bifidobacterium longum on Insulin Sensitivity in Subjects with Obesity.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1101/2025.06.23.25327556
A1  - Baeuerle, Eric
A1  - Semwal, Manpreet K
A1  - Nie, Jia
A1  - Zhang, Ning
A1  - Liang, Hanyu
A1  - Ganapathy, Vinutha
A1  - Sathavarodom, Nattapol
A1  - Fernandez, Roman
