T1  - Nicotinamide Adenine Dinucleotide Augmentation in Overweight or Obese Middle-Aged and Older Adults: A Physiologic Study.
T3  - Comment in: J Clin Endocrinol Metab. 2023 Aug 18;108(9):e897-e898. doi: 10.1210/clinem/dgad120. PMID: 36869827 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/36869827]
