T1  - Leptin increases hepatic triglyceride export via a vagal mechanism in humans.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.cmet.2022.09.020
A1  - Metz, Matthaus
A1  - Beghini, Marianna
A1  - Wolf, Peter
A1  - Pfleger, Lorenz
