T1  - Ertugliflozin to reduce arrhythmic burden in ICD/CRT patients (ERASe-trial) - A phase III study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ahj.2022.01.008
A1  - von Lewinski, Dirk
A1  - Tripolt, Norbert J
A1  - Sourij, Harald
