T1  - Combined Metabolic Activators Accelerates Recovery in Mild-to-Moderate COVID-19.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1002/advs.202101222
A1  - Altay, Ozlem
A1  - Arif, Muhammad
A1  - Li, Xiangyu
A1  - Yang, Hong
A1  - Aydin, Mehtap
A1  - Alkurt, Gizem
A1  - Kim, Woonghee
A1  - Akyol, Dogukan
