T1  - Adherence and Dietary Composition during Intermittent vs. Continuous Calorie Restriction: Follow-Up Data from a Randomized Controlled Trial in Adults with Overweight or Obesity.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3390/nu13041195
A1  - Pannen, Sarah T
A1  - Maldonado, Sandra Gonzalez
A1  - Nonnenmacher, Tobias
A1  - Sowah, Solomon A
A1  - Gruner, Laura F
A1  - Watzinger, Cora
