T1  - Nicotinamide mononucleotide increases muscle insulin sensitivity in prediabetic women.
T3  - Comment in: Science. 2021 Jun 11;372(6547):1147-1148. doi: 10.1126/science.abj0764 PMID: 34112679 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34112679] Comment in: Cell Metab. 2021 Jul 6;33(7):1274-1275. doi: 10.1016/j.cmet.2021.06.008 PMID: 34233170 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34233170] Comment in: Cardiovasc Res. 2021 Jul 27;117(9):e106-e109. doi: 10.1093/cvr/cvab212 PMID: 34320167 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34320167] Comment in: Science. 2021 Jul 30;373(6554):eabj1696. doi: 10.1126/science.abj1696 PMID: 34326206 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34326206]
