T1  - Biochemical metabolism of young plants of Ucuuba (Virola surinamensis) in the presence of cadmium.
T3  - Erratum in: BMC Plant Biol. 2021 Apr 8;21(1):168. doi: 10.1186/s12870-021-02950-6 PMID: 33832429 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33832429]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s12870-021-02912-y
A1  - Junior, W V Andrade
A1  - Neto, C F Oliveira
A1  - Filho, B G Santos
A1  - Cruz, E D
