T1  - Pembrolizumab as a monotherapy or in combination with platinum-based chemotherapy in advanced non-small cell lung cancer with PD-L1 tumor proportion score (TPS) >=50%: real-world data.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1080/2162402X.2020.1865653
A1  - Dudnik, Elizabeth
A1  - Moskovitz, Mor
A1  - Rottenberg, Yakir
A1  - Lobachov, Anastasiya
A1  - Mandelboim, Rinat
A1  - Shochat, Tzippy
