T1  - Nicotinamide riboside does not alter mitochondrial respiration, content or morphology in skeletal muscle from obese and insulin-resistant men.
T3  - Comment in: J Physiol. 2020 Feb;598(4):619-620. doi: 10.1113/JP279280 PMID: 31879956 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31879956] Comment in: J Physiol. 2020 Aug;598(16):3327-3328. doi: 10.1113/JP279749 PMID: 32463114 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32463114]
