T1  - Effect of oral administration of nicotinamide mononucleotide on clinical parameters and nicotinamide metabolite levels in healthy Japanese men.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1507/endocrj.EJ19-0313
A1  - Irie, Junichiro
