T1  - Clinical and MRI responses to etanercept in early non-radiographic axial spondyloarthritis: 48-week results from the EMBARK study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/annrheumdis-2015-207596
A1  - Maksymowych, Walter P
A1  - Dougados, Maxime
A1  - van der Heijde, Desiree
A1  - Sieper, Joachim
A1  - Braun, Jurgen
A1  - Citera, Gustavo
A1  - Van den Bosch, Filip
A1  - Logeart, Isabelle
A1  - Wajdula, Joseph
