T1  - Integrated Biomarker and Imaging Study 3 (IBIS-3) to assess the ability of rosuvastatin to decrease necrotic core in coronary arteries.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.4244/EIJV12I6A118
A1  - Oemrawsingh, Rohit M
A1  - Garcia-Garcia, Hector M
A1  - van Geuns, Robert J M
A1  - Lenzen, Mattie J
A1  - Simsek, Cihan
