T1  - "A randomized, double-blind study of the effects of omega-3 fatty acids (Omegaven) on outcome after major liver resection".
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s12876-015-0331-1
A1  - Linecker, Michael
A1  - Limani, Perparim
A1  - Botea, Florin
A1  - Popescu, Irinel
A1  - Alikhanov, Ruslan
