T1  - Evidence for a direct effect of the NAD+ precursor acipimox on muscle mitochondrial function in humans.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.2337/db14-0667
A1  - van de Weijer, Tineke
A1  - Phielix, Esther
A1  - Bilet, Lena
A1  - Williams, Evan G
A1  - Ropelle, Eduardo R
A1  - Bierwagen, Alessandra
A1  - Livingstone, Roshan
A1  - Nowotny, Peter
A1  - Sparks, Lauren M
