T1  - Consistently Good clinical response in patients with early axial spondyloarthritis after 3 years of continuous treatment with etanercept: longterm data of the ESTHER trial.
T3  - Comment in: J Rheumatol. 2014 Oct;41(10):1899-902. doi: 10.3899/jrheum.140866 PMID: 25275090 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25275090]
