T1  - Efficacy and safety of adalimumab in patients with non-radiographic axial spondyloarthritis: results of a randomised placebo-controlled trial (ABILITY-1).
T3  - Comment in: Ann Rheum Dis. 2013 Jun;72(6):789-90. doi: 10.1136/annrheumdis-2012-202908. PMID: 23667168 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23667168] Comment in: Ann Rheum Dis. 2015 Mar;74(3):e21. doi: 10.1136/annrheumdis-2014-206811. PMID: 25371443 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25371443]
