T1  - Impact of pressure profile and duration of recruitment maneuvers on morphofunctional and biochemical variables in experimental lung injury.
T3  - Comment in: Crit Care Med. 2011 May;39(5):1221-2. doi: 10.1097/CCM.0b013e31820a4dc7 PMID: 21610587 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21610587]
