T1  - Precise prediction model and simplified scoring system for sustained combined response to interferon-alpha.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3748/wjg.v16.i27.3465
A1  - Mao, Qian-Guo
A1  - Pan, Jin-Shui
A1  - Fang, Kuang-Nan
